Scenario: Removing Group Skills
	Given Navigation Views Page
	When I click on Skils Menu Navigation Bar
	And I click on View Group Skils sub Menu item
	Then I can see a select box with values
	When I choose Group Id and click to Search 
	Then I can view all the skils of a Particular Group
	When I click on the remove option
	Then skills are deleted
